{"title":"HOODIES","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"rules-breaker-hoodie","title":"RULES BREAKER HOODIE","description":"\u003cp\u003e 420 GSM\u003cbr\u003e PREMIUM 100% COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; MATTE BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e “RULES BREAKER” PREMIUM SCREEN PRINT\u003cbr\u003e YKK SILVER ZIPPER CLOSURE\u003cbr\u003e KANGAROO POCKETS\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eUltra-heavy 420 GSM cotton fleece delivers superior structure, warmth, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eIntricate “Rules Breaker” premium screen print creates a bold, statement-driven look.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eCombed and matte bio-washed finish ensures exceptional softness and long-lasting color depth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eAuthentic YKK silver zipper provides smooth functionality and premium durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStructured construction designed for elevated everyday wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFunctional kangaroo pockets add warmth and daily utility.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing enhances all-day comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBuilt as a statement zip hoodie blending craftsmanship with streetwear authority.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the hoodie inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain shape and prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to protect the fabric and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eHoodie constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial, premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBaggy fit for relaxed, comfortable, and versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFront pouch pocket for convenience and added warmth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eLong sleeves with ribbed cuffs and hem for a secure, structured fit.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46880663634074,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46880663666842,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46880663699610,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46880663732378,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46880663765146,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46880663797914,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_5553_1__11zon_8885cec2-1517-4f88-9084-ba624823b8da.webp?v=1768931343"},{"product_id":"unholy-saint","title":"UNHOLY SAINT ♡","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eMALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32  WEARING M HOODIE.\r\n\r\n420 GSM\r\nPIPING WORK OVER SHOULDER, ARMS AND WAIST AREA\r\nPREMIUM 100% COTTON MATERIAL\r\nEMBROIDERY PRINT FRONT AND BACK (78,000+ embroidery stitches)\r\nBAGGY FIT [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS].\r\nCOMBED AND BIOWASHED.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStep into elevated streetwear with this 420 GSM super-premium sweatshirt, crafted for comfort, durability, and bold style. Made using combed and bio-washed fabric, it delivers a smooth, soft feel with long-lasting quality. The design features sleek piping work running across the shoulders, arms, and waist, adding a sharp, structured look. Front and back high-density embroidery make a strong statement, showcasing intricate detailing that stands out. With its relaxed fit, this sweatshirt blends effortless vibe with premium construction—perfect for everyday wear or standout street style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Machine wash the sweatshirt inside out with like colors.\r\n* Use cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\n* Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\n* Store the sweatshirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Sweatshirt with 420 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\n* Baggy fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\n* Unisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\n* Front pouch pocket for convenient storage and added warmth.\r\n* Soft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\r\n* Long sleeves and ribbed cuffs and hem provide a snug and stylish fit.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853858197658,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853858230426,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853858263194,"