ual identity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the hoodie inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain shape and prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to protect the fabric and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eHoodie constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial, premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBaggy fit designed for relaxed comfort and versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFront pouch pocket for everyday convenience and warmth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eLong sleeves with ribbed cuffs and hem for a secure, structured fit.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853859246234,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"S","offer_id":46853859082394,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853859115162,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853859147930,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853859180698,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2678.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853859213466,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-C