ocket provides warmth and daily utility.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures all-day comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBuilt as a statement hoodie that balances intent, style, and longevity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the hoodie inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain shape and prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to preserve structure and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eHoodie constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial, premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBaggy fit suitable for relaxed and versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article designed for a wide range of body types.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFront pouch pocket for everyday convenience and warmth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey fabric promotes comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eLong sleeves with ribbed cuffs and hem for a secure, structured fit.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e\n","brand":"dripdrip.dopedesk","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46939960869018,"sku":null,"price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46939960901786,"sku":null,"price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46939960934554,"sku":null,"price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46939960967322,"sku":null,"price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2XL","offer_id":46939961000090,"sku":null,"price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/FE4EDC01-74F4-49A1-B34E-BF5